+-- ------------------------------------------------------------------------
+-- Tracker frame component scale: scales SC Icon, Sequence Icon Scroll,
+-- and Tracker Text together as a group. Independent of the parent widget
+-- scale above; each of the 3 frames receives :SetScale(value) directly.
